{"tid":2487314,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Audi Q3 新車","createTime":"2021-04-13T12:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T13:50:55.000Z","uid":222054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b583c5a20d157dae23eac1cd2b679e9a5c296170","tid":2487314,"uid":222054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:43:19.000Z","msg":"先利申：新手第一次買車買一手車<br />\n<br />\nShowroom 睇過Q3<br />\n車款、內籠、車廂空間都啱自己心水<br />\n問題係應該買邊一個版本<br />\n35 TSFI 定 45 TFSI Quattro <br />\n<br />\n自問對馬力要求唔高，前驅150匹定四驅230匹都冇所謂，主要都係做腳車加假日車老婆同狗狗去遠啲玩<br />\n<br />\n35 TFSI 賣 380k 但原來好多配備想加錢加option 都冇，例如 360鏡頭、cruise control、hill descent control, MMI navigation<br />\n45 TSFI Quattro 賣正價 470k有得加option，但加埋option 近500k，就嚟q5 都買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實q3級數嘅車應該已經好夠用，但買得新車就係想有齊一架新車應有嘅設備<br />\n<br />\n係咪真係值得攞多120k 換有埋Quattro 加完整車廂設備<br />\n定拎得咁嘅價錢出嚟不如Benz GLA, BMW X3 或者Q5 好過<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外其實另一部睇中嘅係Volvo xc40 inscription<br />\n賣420k 齊晒所有options <br />\n但代理話而家訂車要7 8月先有得攞<br />\n加上 Volvo 大老闆係...你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b15a37e38363113fc32a6700db87a14765892f","tid":2487314,"uid":227869,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"新手買新車 你唔到一個月就會後悔 未操熟好易揩花"},{"pid":"b97bb8843609c63fc33fa6773c0b5c4250b9f963","tid":2487314,"uid":214644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:46:01.000Z","msg":"Volvo xc40真係幾有誠意"},{"pid":"32dcd6cc41a900d423ff8f81c153489cd4ddd449","tid":2487314,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:48:59.000Z","msg":"差90k <br />\n如果budget夠 <br />\n唔加option買45都有so"},{"pid":"79aceb9276bf5666dec8616dc286fe9977ae0c70","tid":2487314,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"不過好老實<br />\n不如問sales買上代A3 40 TFSI 貨尾"},{"pid":"5